## Outputs

Write to `sign/{language}/linguistics/`:

| File | Contents |
|------|----------|
| `ARCHITECTURE.md` | Encoding choice + rationale, catalog scope, validation panel |
| `HANDSHAPES.yaml` | Phonemic handshape inventory, contrast pairs, variants |
| `LOCATIONS.yaml` | Body-relative location grid + contact / proximity rules |
| `MOVEMENTS.yaml` | Path + local movement primitives, coarticulation defaults |
| `NON-MANUAL.yaml` | Non-manual markers, grammatical functions, scope |
| `PROSODY.yaml` | Intensity, repetition, hold, speed, pause distributions |
| `BIBLIOGRAPHY.md` | Every primary source with DOI/URL and what part of the catalog it supports |
| `VALIDATION.md` | Native-signer panel composition, disagreements, resolution log |

